1
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:03,760
Sanniang.

2
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,200
Sanniang, what's wrong?

3
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,120
Is this okay?

4
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,480
Acting.

5
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:19,320
The chicken blood looks like that.

6
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,760
I'll go to see Suqin tomorrow morning.

7
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:22,960
You need to do your best

8
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,880
to make things clear.

9
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,880
The soup is cold.

10
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,320
I'll get you another one.

11
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,000
It's okay. There are snacks here.

12
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:38,920
The dessert is spilled.

13
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,000
I'll get you another one.

14
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,000
insecticide.

15
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,120
Don't worry.

16
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,479
I'm glad she's fine.

17
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,880
I have nothing against Chuntao.

18
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,240
I must have been forced by Jiang Yingying again.

19
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,800
But we have no evidence now.

20
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:06,200
We need to put on a show to make her reveal her flaws.

21
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:10,120
So, do you have a plan?

22
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,160
You love reading so much.

23
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:15,560
You must know there's a plan in the book of war.

24
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:17,680
It's called playing along.

25
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:27,360
Xiuqin, what's wrong with my wife?

26
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,000
She's poisoned.

27
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,280
She might be in danger.

28
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,400
How could this happen?

29
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,480
You have to save her.

30
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,800
How can I live without her?

31
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,920
Wenjun.

32
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,680
You were fine before.

33
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,280
Why is she suddenly like this?

34
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:41,840
She...

35
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,160
What poison did she get?

36
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,880
How should I put it?

37
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:49,400
Can my wife be saved?

38
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,320
Don't eat water anymore.

39
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,840
Otherwise, you won't survive tonight.

40
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,320
What?

41
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,520
Take good care of her.

42
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,120
If anything goes wrong today,

43
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,120
you'll die for sure.

44
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,320
My lady.

45
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,680
Sanniang.

46
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:22,040
You did a good job.

47
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,120
It's just not clean enough.

48
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:27,760
I don't like to be hesitant.

49
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:30,320
It's over tonight.

50
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:31,440
But Miss,

51
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:34,840
General Xu is no longer a threat.

52
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,120
I'm sorry.

53
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:38,960
I was wrong.

54
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,240
I'm sorry.

55
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,760
I'm sorry.

56
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:43,920
Please spare me.

57
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,120
Spare me.

58
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:47,079
I want her to die tonight.

59
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,640
You'd better not let me down.

60
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:53,200
Don't forget that your mother is still

61
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,640
in my mansion.

62
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,440
I'll do it right away.

63
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:18,720
You're so persistent.

64
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,760
How many times have you killed me?

65
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:20,839
Why don't you give up?

66
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,760
You wanted to kill me.

67
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,120
not me.

68
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,320
I didn't cry.

69
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,280
Why are you crying?

70
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:34,720
Did Jiang Yingying send you here?

71
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,360
Since she's ready to leave,

72
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,920
why did she do this?

73
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,480
Miss.

74
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,680
She said as long as General Xu is here,

75
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,560
everyone would think it was the Crown Prince.

76
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,159
and abandoned her for a village woman.

77
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:50,440
she will always be the laughing stock in the capital.

78
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:51,560
So...

79
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,720
So...

80
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:56,480
General Xu, I didn't mean to kill you.

81
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,640
This is just the antidote for insect-killing poison.

82
00:04:58,640 --> 00:05:00,280
I want to save you

83
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,040
and put on a show for me.

84
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,000
and hide it from you.

85
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,680
I really didn't want to kill you.

86
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:11,920
It's the antidote.

87
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:16,360
Jiang Yingying did the scar on your arm, right?

88
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,280
She did this to you.

89
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,320
why did you help her kill?

90
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:22,480
My indenture is in the Prime Minister’s Mansion.

91
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,320
After my family fell,

92
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,880
after my family fell.

93
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:28,120
My parents work in the Prime Minister’s Mansion.

94
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,640
If I don't listen to you,

95
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,840
my parents won't survive.

96
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,120
I've sent someone to investigate.

97
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:36,880
Your parents were killed

98
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:38,560
by Jiang Yingying.

99
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,920
This is a document from the Ministry of Revenue.

100
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,120
What?

101
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:59,440
Chuntao, I'm willing to tell you everything.

102
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,480
What happened?

103
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:10,520
Did Chuntao do something wrong?

104
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,920
and upset you?

105
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:14,400
Jiang Yingying, what is this?

106
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,320
What do you mean?

107
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,440
It's between you and me.

108
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,920
you can take it out on me.

109
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,320
Why do you involve others?

110
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,320
You bitch!

111
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,280
What did you say?

112
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,680
How dare you betray me?

113
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,920
If it weren't for Chun Tao,

114
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:28,280
you would be a murderer now.

115
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:31,120
Jiang Yingying, as a member of the palace,

116
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,480
you don't set an example for the people,

117
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,760
but harm the people.

118
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,280
Don't be so arrogant.

119
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,960
You humiliated me.

120
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,680
and become a laughing stock in the capital.

121
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,280
Now you're here to pretend to be a good person.

122
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,320
Why don't you think

123
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,200
losing the person I love

124
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:48,320
