130
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:04,760
Jiang Yingying, you can't stay in Gusu County anymore.

131
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,880
Make yourself at home.

132
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:11,120
Xu Sanniang, don't think that you won.

133
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,480
We have plenty of time.

134
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,520
You probably can't go back.

135
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,280
Just stay in Gusu County.

136
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,240
It's okay.

137
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,640
Don't be afraid.

138
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,760
You are good at medicine.

139
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:26,320
Just stay in my pharmacy.

140
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:54,920
