141
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,680
Father.

142
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:58,680
Governor of Gusu expelled me from the city.

143
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,120
That Xu Sanniang...

144
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,760
