164
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:37,799
Okay.

165
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,039
Good.

166
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,880
Let's follow the plan.

167
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,400
