168
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,800
Let the Japanese enter Gusu County.

169
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:50,000
Leave the matter of Xu Qianqing colluding with bandits to Gusu County.

170
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,560
You're wise, Eunuch.

171
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:54,360
I'll report to His Majesty now.

172
